narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend Spanish 120. You will be able to speak adequately by the end of the semester.
Spanish 120 is basically a continuation of Spanish 110. It continues along the same path, but gets more challenging.
I recommend Spanish 120 to anyone looking to dramatically improve their speaking abilities and comprehension.
If Profesora Juliana Ramos-Ruano were teaching L3 at 8 a.m. at the top of Science Hill, I would take her class in a heartbeat. She's that good.
